{
  "video_id": "9y7YEmyz-Do",
  "title": "The global learning crisis -- and what to do about it | Amel Karboul",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13160.0,
      "end_time": 15760.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m the product of a bold leadership decision."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16920.0,
      "end_time": 20896.0,
      "text": "After 1956, when Tunisia became independent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20920.0,
      "end_time": 23656.0,
      "text": "our first president, Habib Bourguiba,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23680.0,
      "end_time": 27536.0,
      "text": "decided to invest 20 percent of the country&#39;s national budget"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27560.0,
      "end_time": 29136.0,
      "text": "in education."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29160.0,
      "end_time": 30736.0,
      "text": "Yes, 20 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30760.0,
      "end_time": 33920.0,
      "text": "on the high end of the spectrum even by today&#39;s standards."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34480.0,
      "end_time": 36376.0,
      "text": "Some people protested."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36400.0,
      "end_time": 38960.0,
      "text": "What about infrastructure?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38120.0,
      "end_time": 41135.0,
      "text": "What about electricity, roads and running water?"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41160.0,
      "end_time": 42519.0,
      "text": "Are these not important?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44159.0,
      "end_time": 45616.0,
      "text": "I would argue"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45640.0,
      "end_time": 49320.0,
      "text": "that the most important infrastructure we have are minds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50360.0,
      "end_time": 51640.0,
      "text": "educated minds."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53280.0,
      "end_time": 59496.0,
      "text": "President Bourguiba helped establish free, high-quality education"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59520.0,
      "end_time": 61840.0,
      "text": "for every boy and every girl."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 63760.0,
      "end_time": 66816.0,
      "text": "And together with millions of other Tunisians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66840.0,
      "end_time": 69360.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m deeply indebted to that historic decision."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 70400.0,
      "end_time": 72160.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s what brought me here today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 73280.0,
      "end_time": 77200.0,
      "text": "because today, we are facing a global learning crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77840.0,
      "end_time": 81176.0,
      "text": "I call it learning crisis and not education crisis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 81200.0,
      "end_time": 84136.0,
      "text": "because on top of the quarter of a billion children"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 84160.0,
      "end_time": 85759.0,
      "text": "who are out of school today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 86800.0,
      "end_time": 90856.0,
      "text": "even more, 330 million children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 90880.0,
      "end_time": 93679.0,
      "text": "are in school but failing to learn."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 95760.0,
      "end_time": 97576.0,
      "text": "And if we do nothing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 97600.0,
      "end_time": 99256.0,
      "text": "if nothing changes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 99280.0,
      "end_time": 103256.0,
      "text": "by 2030, just 13 years from now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 103280.0,
      "end_time": 106816.0,
      "text": "half of the world&#39;s children and youth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 106840.0,
      "end_time": 110896.0,
      "text": "half of 1.6 billion children and youth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 110920.0,
      "end_time": 113760.0,
      "text": "will be either out of school or failing to learn."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 118240.0,
      "end_time": 122560.0,
      "text": "So two years ago, I joined the Education Commission."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 122800.0,
      "end_time": 125816.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a commission brought together by former UK Prime Minister"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 125840.0,
      "end_time": 128759.0,
      "text": "and UN Special Envoy for Global Education Gordon Brown."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 129960.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132160.0,
      "text": "Our first task was to find out:"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 132400.0,
      "end_time": 133696.0,
      "text": "How big is the learning crisis?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 133720.0,
      "end_time": 135680.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s actually the scope of the problem?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 136840.0,
      "end_time": 138296.0,
      "text": "Today we know:"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 138320.0,
      "end_time": 141495.0,
      "text": "half of the world&#39;s children by 2030"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 141520.0,
      "end_time": 142840.0,
      "text": "will be failing to learn."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 144000.0,
      "end_time": 145936.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s how actually we discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 145960.0,
      "end_time": 150656.0,
      "text": "that we need to change the world&#39;s focus from schooling to learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 150680.0,
      "end_time": 153416.0,
      "text": "from just counting how many bodies are in classrooms"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 153440.0,
      "end_time": 155120.0,
      "text": "to actually how many are learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 156320.0,
      "end_time": 158320.0,
      "text": "And the second big task was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 159520.0,
      "end_time": 160960.0,
      "text": "can we do anything about this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 161760.0,
      "end_time": 165176.0,
      "text": "Can we do anything about this big, vast, silent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 165200.0,
      "end_time": 168790.0,
      "text": "maybe most-neglected international crisis?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 168640.0,
      "end_time": 171815.0,
      "text": "And what we found out is, we can."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 171840.0,
      "end_time": 173400.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s actually amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 174000.0,
      "end_time": 176176.0,
      "text": "We can, for the first time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 176200.0,
      "end_time": 179816.0,
      "text": "have every child in school and learning"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 179840.0,
      "end_time": 182200.0,
      "text": "within just one generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 183840.0,
      "end_time": 186640.0,
      "text": "And we don&#39;t even have to really invent the wheel to do so."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 187600.0,
      "end_time": 190736.0,
      "text": "We just need to learn from the best in class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 190760.0,
      "end_time": 193550.0,
      "text": "but not any best in class --"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 193800.0,
      "end_time": 194880.0,
      "text": "the best in your own class."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 196200.0,
      "end_time": 199935.0,
      "text": "What we did is actually we looked at countries by income level:"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 199960.0,
      "end_time": 202696.0,
      "text": "low-income, mid-income, high-income."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 202720.0,
      "end_time": 206960.0,
      "text": "We looked at what the 25 percent fastest improvers in education do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 207760.0,
      "end_time": 209655.0,
      "text": "and what we found out is"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 209680.0,
      "end_time": 214176.0,
      "text": "that if every country moves at the same rate as the fastest improvers"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 214200.0,
      "end_time": 216655.0,
      "text": "within their own income level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 216680.0,
      "end_time": 219560.0,
      "text": "then within just one generation"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 219800.0,
      "end_time": 221760.0,
      "text": "we can have every child in school and learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 223880.0,
      "end_time": 225976.0,
      "text": "Let me give you an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 226000.0,
      "end_time": 227936.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take Tunisia for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 227960.0,
      "end_time": 231736.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re not telling Tunisia, \"You should move as fast as Finland.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 231760.0,
      "end_time": 233696.0,
      "text": "No disrespect, Finland."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 233720.0,
      "end_time": 235960.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re telling Tunisia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 235120.0,
      "end_time": 236456.0,
      "text": "\"Look at Vietnam.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 236480.0,
      "end_time": 240816.0,
      "text": "They spend similar amounts for primary and secondary pupils"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 240840.0,
      "end_time": 243136.0,
      "text": "as percentage of GDP per capita,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 243160.0,
      "end_time": 245000.0,
      "text": "but achieves today higher results."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 246440.0,
      "end_time": 250320.0,
      "text": "Vietnam introduced a standardized assessment for literacy and numeracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 251120.0,
      "end_time": 255856.0,
      "text": "teachers in Vietnam are better monitored than in other developing countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 255880.0,
      "end_time": 258480.0,
      "text": "and students&#39; achievements are made public."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 260000.0,
      "end_time": 261519.0,
      "text": "And it shows in the results."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 262160.0,
      "end_time": 264960.0,
      "text": "In the 2015 PISA --"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 264120.0,
      "end_time": 266776.0,
      "text": "Program for International Student Assessment --"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 266800.0,
      "end_time": 269616.0,
      "text": "Vietnam outperformed many wealthy economies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 269640.0,
      "end_time": 271519.0,
      "text": "including the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 273680.0,
      "end_time": 276696.0,
      "text": "Now, if you&#39;re not an education expert,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 276720.0,
      "end_time": 278656.0,
      "text": "you may ask, \"What&#39;s new and different?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 278680.0,
      "end_time": 283120.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t all countries track student progress and make those achievements public?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 284400.0,
      "end_time": 286976.0,
      "text": "No. The sad answer is no."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 287000.0,
      "end_time": 288560.0,
      "text": "We are very far from it."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 289400.0,
      "end_time": 291895.0,
      "text": "Only half of the developing countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 291920.0,
      "end_time": 294936.0,
      "text": "have systematic learning assessment at primary school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 294960.0,
      "end_time": 297880.0,
      "text": "and even less so at lower secondary school."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 299800.0,
      "end_time": 302335.0,
      "text": "So if we don&#39;t know"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 302360.0,
      "end_time": 304560.0,
      "text": "if children are learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 304800.0,
      "end_time": 308150.0,
      "text": "how are teachers supposed to focus their attention on delivering results,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 308400.0,
      "end_time": 311616.0,
      "text": "and how are countries supposed to prioritize education spending"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 311640.0,
      "end_time": 313135.0,
      "text": "actually to delivering results,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 313160.0,
      "end_time": 315240.0,
      "text": "if they don&#39;t know if children are learning?"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 316600.0,
      "end_time": 320456.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why the first big transformation"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 320480.0,
      "end_time": 322256.0,
      "text": "before investing"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 322280.0,
      "end_time": 325479.0,
      "text": "is to make the education system deliver results."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 327160.0,
      "end_time": 330896.0,
      "text": "Because pouring more money into broken systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 330920.0,
      "end_time": 332840.0,
      "text": "may only fund more inefficiencies."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 334240.0,
      "end_time": 336560.0,
      "text": "And what deeply worries me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 336800.0,
      "end_time": 339296.0,
      "text": "if children go to school and don&#39;t learn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 339320.0,
      "end_time": 341560.0,
      "text": "it devalues education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 341800.0,
      "end_time": 343256.0,
      "text": "and it devalues spending on education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 343280.0,
      "end_time": 345976.0,
      "text": "so that governments and political parties can say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 346000.0,
      "end_time": 348256.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, we are spending so much money on education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 348280.0,
      "end_time": 349736.0,
      "text": "but children are not learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 349760.0,
      "end_time": 351736.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t have the right skills."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 351760.0,
      "end_time": 353440.0,
      "text": "Maybe we should spend less.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 354800.0,
      "end_time": 358695.0,
      "text": "Now, improving current education systems to deliver results"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 358720.0,
      "end_time": 360800.0,
      "text": "is important, but won&#39;t be enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 362000.0,
      "end_time": 365176.0,
      "text": "What about countries where we won&#39;t have enough qualified teachers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 365200.0,
      "end_time": 366455.0,
      "text": "Take Somalia, for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 366480.0,
      "end_time": 369496.0,
      "text": "If every student in Somalia became a teacher --"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 369520.0,
      "end_time": 372616.0,
      "text": "every person who finishes tertiary education became a teacher --"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 372640.0,
      "end_time": 374680.0,
      "text": "we won&#39;t have enough teachers."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 376160.0,
      "end_time": 379216.0,
      "text": "And what about children in refugee camps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 379240.0,
      "end_time": 381240.0,
      "text": "or in very remote rural areas?"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 382280.0,
      "end_time": 383719.0,
      "text": "Take Filipe, for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 384480.0,
      "end_time": 387696.0,
      "text": "Filipe lives in one of the thousands of communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 387720.0,
      "end_time": 389720.0,
      "text": "alongside the Amazonas rivers."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 390400.0,
      "end_time": 393679.0,
      "text": "His village of 78 people has 20 families."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 394680.0,
      "end_time": 396496.0,
      "text": "Filipe and a fellow student"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 396520.0,
      "end_time": 399599.0,
      "text": "were the only two attending grade 11 in 2015."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 401800.0,
      "end_time": 405960.0,
      "text": "Now, the Amazonas is a state in the northwest of Brazil."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 405120.0,
      "end_time": 407736.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s four and a half times the size of Germany,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 407760.0,
      "end_time": 410390.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s fully covered in jungle and rivers."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 411120.0,
      "end_time": 413936.0,
      "text": "A decade ago, Filipe and his fellow student"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 413960.0,
      "end_time": 415760.0,
      "text": "would have had just two alternatives:"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 417000.0,
      "end_time": 421176.0,
      "text": "moving to Manaus, the capital, or stopping studying altogether,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 421200.0,
      "end_time": 422440.0,
      "text": "which most of them did."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 424600.0,
      "end_time": 428160.0,
      "text": "In 2009, however, Brazil passed a new law"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 428400.0,
      "end_time": 432576.0,
      "text": "that made secondary education a guarantee for every Brazilian"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 432600.0,
      "end_time": 436320.0,
      "text": "and an obligation for every state to implement this by 2016."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 437600.0,
      "end_time": 440816.0,
      "text": "But giving access to high-quality education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 440840.0,
      "end_time": 443536.0,
      "text": "you know, in the Amazonas state, is huge and expensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 443560.0,
      "end_time": 447160.0,
      "text": "How are you going to get, you know, math and science and history teachers"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 447400.0,
      "end_time": 448376.0,
      "text": "all over those communities?"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 448400.0,
      "end_time": 450150.0,
      "text": "And even if you find them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 450400.0,
      "end_time": 452800.0,
      "text": "many of them would not want to move there."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 453440.0,
      "end_time": 455976.0,
      "text": "So faced with this impossible task,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 456000.0,
      "end_time": 458336.0,
      "text": "civil servants and state officials"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 458360.0,
      "end_time": 461360.0,
      "text": "developed amazing creativity and entrepreneurship."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 462120.0,
      "end_time": 464960.0,
      "text": "They developed the media center solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 464120.0,
      "end_time": 465376.0,
      "text": "It works this way."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 465400.0,
      "end_time": 470816.0,
      "text": "You have specialized, trained content teachers in Manaus"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 470840.0,
      "end_time": 473215.0,
      "text": "delivering classroom via livestream"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 473240.0,
      "end_time": 476400.0,
      "text": "to over a thousand classrooms in those scattered communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 477160.0,
      "end_time": 480256.0,
      "text": "Those classrooms have five to 25 students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 480280.0,
      "end_time": 483895.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re supported by a more generalist tutoring teacher"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 483920.0,
      "end_time": 485600.0,
      "text": "for their learning and development."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 486480.0,
      "end_time": 488816.0,
      "text": "The 60 content teachers in Manaus"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 488840.0,
      "end_time": 494296.0,
      "text": "work with over 2,200 tutoring teachers in those communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 494320.0,
      "end_time": 497240.0,
      "text": "to customize lesson plans to the context and time."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 499440.0,
      "end_time": 501376.0,
      "text": "Now, why is this division"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 501400.0,
      "end_time": 505000.0,
      "text": "between content teacher and tutoring teacher important?"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 506600.0,
      "end_time": 509216.0,
      "text": "First of all, as I told you, because in many countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 509240.0,
      "end_time": 511896.0,
      "text": "we just don&#39;t have enough qualified teachers."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 511920.0,
      "end_time": 515216.0,
      "text": "But secondly also because teachers do too many things"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 515240.0,
      "end_time": 517760.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re either not trained for or not supposed to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 519390.0,
      "end_time": 520719.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s look at Chile, for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 521558.99999999994,
      "end_time": 523694.99999999994,
      "text": "In Chile, for every doctor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 523720.0,
      "end_time": 525655.0,
      "text": "you have four and a half people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 525679.0,
      "end_time": 527760.0,
      "text": "four and a half staff supporting them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 528520.0,
      "end_time": 533856.0,
      "text": "and Chile is on the low end of the spectrum here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 533880.0,
      "end_time": 536616.0,
      "text": "because in developing countries, on average, every doctor"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 536640.0,
      "end_time": 538240.0,
      "text": "has 10 people supporting them."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 539720.0,
      "end_time": 541656.0,
      "text": "A teacher in Chile, however,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 541680.0,
      "end_time": 544415.0,
      "text": "has less than half a person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 544440.0,
      "end_time": 547400.0,
      "text": "0.3 persons, supporting them."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 548360.0,
      "end_time": 552736.0,
      "text": "Imagine a hospital ward with 20, 40, 70 patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 552760.0,
      "end_time": 555816.0,
      "text": "and you have a doctor doing it all by themselves:"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 555840.0,
      "end_time": 558256.0,
      "text": "no nurses, no medical assistants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 558280.0,
      "end_time": 559480.0,
      "text": "no one else."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 560360.0,
      "end_time": 562696.0,
      "text": "You will say this is absurd and impossible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 562720.0,
      "end_time": 566216.0,
      "text": "but this is what teachers are doing all over the world every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 566240.0,
      "end_time": 568960.0,
      "text": "with classrooms of 20, 40, or 70 students."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 570400.0,
      "end_time": 574160.0,
      "text": "So this division between content and tutoring teachers is amazing"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 574400.0,
      "end_time": 576976.0,
      "text": "because it is changing the paradigm of the teacher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 577000.0,
      "end_time": 579216.0,
      "text": "so that each does what they can do best"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 579240.0,
      "end_time": 581456.0,
      "text": "and so that children are not just in school"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 581480.0,
      "end_time": 583800.0,
      "text": "but in school and learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 584640.0,
      "end_time": 586576.0,
      "text": "And some of these content teachers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 586600.0,
      "end_time": 588776.0,
      "text": "they became celebrity teachers."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 588800.0,
      "end_time": 590656.0,
      "text": "You know, some of them run for office,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 590680.0,
      "end_time": 593496.0,
      "text": "and they helped raise the status of the profession"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 593520.0,
      "end_time": 595920.0,
      "text": "so that more students wanted to become teachers."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 597960.0,
      "end_time": 599976.0,
      "text": "And what I love about this example"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 600000.0,
      "end_time": 603376.0,
      "text": "is beyond changing the paradigm of the teacher."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 603400.0,
      "end_time": 606400.0,
      "text": "It teaches us how we can harness technology for learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 607400.0,
      "end_time": 609776.0,
      "text": "The live-streaming is bidirectional,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 609800.0,
      "end_time": 613319.0,
      "text": "so students like Filipe and others can present information back."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 614360.0,
      "end_time": 617216.0,
      "text": "And we know technology is not always perfect."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 617240.0,
      "end_time": 618816.0,
      "text": "You know, state officials expect"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 618840.0,
      "end_time": 620936.0,
      "text": "between five to 15 percent of the classrooms"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 620960.0,
      "end_time": 623560.0,
      "text": "every day to be off live-stream"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 623800.0,
      "end_time": 626280.0,
      "text": "because of flood, broken antennas or internet not working."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 627160.0,
      "end_time": 631935.0,
      "text": "And yet, Filipe is one of over 300,000 students"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 631960.0,
      "end_time": 634136.0,
      "text": "that benefited from the media center solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 634160.0,
      "end_time": 636600.0,
      "text": "and got access to postprimary education."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 638120.0,
      "end_time": 639976.0,
      "text": "This is a living example"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 640000.0,
      "end_time": 642856.0,
      "text": "how technology is not just an add-on"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 642880.0,
      "end_time": 647496.0,
      "text": "but can be central to learning and can help us bring school to children"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 647520.0,
      "end_time": 649640.0,
      "text": "if we cannot bring children to school."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 653320.0,
      "end_time": 654776.0,
      "text": "Now, I hear you."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 654800.0,
      "end_time": 656216.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re going to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 656240.0,
      "end_time": 659456.0,
      "text": "\"How are we going to implement this all over the world?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 659480.0,
      "end_time": 661160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been in government myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 661400.0,
      "end_time": 665280.0,
      "text": "and have seen how difficult it is even to implement the best ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 666240.0,
      "end_time": 669136.0,
      "text": "So as a commission, we started two initiatives"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 669160.0,
      "end_time": 671400.0,
      "text": "to make the \"Learning Generation\" a reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 672400.0,
      "end_time": 675000.0,
      "text": "The first one is called the Pioneer Country Initiative."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 675560.0,
      "end_time": 678950.0,
      "text": "Over 20 countries from Africa and Asia"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 678120.0,
      "end_time": 681560.0,
      "text": "have committed to make education their priority"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 681800.0,
      "end_time": 684856.0,
      "text": "and to transform their education systems to deliver results."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 684880.0,
      "end_time": 686296.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve trained country leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 686320.0,
      "end_time": 689960.0,
      "text": "in a methodology called the delivery approach."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 689120.0,
      "end_time": 691160.0,
      "text": "What this does is basically two things."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 691400.0,
      "end_time": 694336.0,
      "text": "In the planning phase, we take everyone into a room --"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 694360.0,
      "end_time": 696776.0,
      "text": "teachers, teacher unions, parent associations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 696800.0,
      "end_time": 699335.0,
      "text": "government officials, NGOs, everyone --"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 699360.0,
      "end_time": 701741.0,
      "text": "so that the reform and the solution we come up with"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 701765.0,
      "end_time": 704205.0,
      "text": "are shared by everyone and supported by everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 705320.0,
      "end_time": 707256.0,
      "text": "And in the second phase,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 707280.0,
      "end_time": 709656.0,
      "text": "it does something special."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 709680.0,
      "end_time": 712920.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s kind of a ruthless focus on follow-up."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 714440.0,
      "end_time": 717296.0,
      "text": "So week by week you check,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 717320.0,
      "end_time": 719976.0,
      "text": "has that been done, what was supposed to be done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 720000.0,
      "end_time": 724616.0,
      "text": "and even sometimes sending a person physically to the district or school"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 724640.0,
      "end_time": 728600.0,
      "text": "to check that versus just hoping that it happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 729960.0,
      "end_time": 732376.0,
      "text": "It may sound for many common sense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 732400.0,
      "end_time": 733896.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s not common practice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 733920.0,
      "end_time": 736790.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s why actually many reforms fail."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 738400.0,
      "end_time": 739959.0,
      "text": "It has been piloted in Tanzania,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 740720.0,
      "end_time": 746296.0,
      "text": "and there the pass rate for students in secondary education"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 746320.0,
      "end_time": 750400.0,
      "text": "was increased by 50 percent in just over two years."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 752960.0,
      "end_time": 756536.0,
      "text": "Now, the next initiative to make the Learning Generation a reality"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 756560.0,
      "end_time": 758920.0,
      "text": "is financing. Who&#39;s going to pay for this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 760400.0,
      "end_time": 761456.0,
      "text": "So we believe and argue"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 761480.0,
      "end_time": 765240.0,
      "text": "that domestic financing has to be the backbone of education investment."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 765680.0,
      "end_time": 768256.0,
      "text": "Do you remember when I told you about Vietnam earlier"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 768280.0,
      "end_time": 770680.0,
      "text": "outperforming the United States in PISA?"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 771240.0,
      "end_time": 773376.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s due to a better education system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 773400.0,
      "end_time": 775976.0,
      "text": "but also to Vietnam increasing their investment"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 776000.0,
      "end_time": 779560.0,
      "text": "from seven to 20 percent of their national budget in two decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 781160.0,
      "end_time": 784240.0,
      "text": "But what happens if countries want to borrow money for education?"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 784960.0,
      "end_time": 788176.0,
      "text": "If you wanted to borrow money to build a bridge or a road,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 788200.0,
      "end_time": 790376.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s quite easy and straightforward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 790400.0,
      "end_time": 791840.0,
      "text": "but not for education."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 792680.0,
      "end_time": 796695.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s easier to make a shiny picture of a bridge and show it to everyone"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 796720.0,
      "end_time": 799296.0,
      "text": "than one of an educated mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 799320.0,
      "end_time": 801440.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s kind of a longer term commitment."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 802555.0,
      "end_time": 803935.0,
      "text": "So we came up with a solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 803960.0,
      "end_time": 807136.0,
      "text": "to help countries escape the middle income trap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 807160.0,
      "end_time": 811376.0,
      "text": "countries that are not poor enough or not poor, thankfully, anymore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 811400.0,
      "end_time": 814896.0,
      "text": "that cannot profit from grants or interest-free loans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 814920.0,
      "end_time": 816415.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re not rich enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 816440.0,
      "end_time": 819400.0,
      "text": "to be able to have attractive interests on their loans."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 819920.0,
      "end_time": 823856.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re pooling donor money in a finance facility for education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 823880.0,
      "end_time": 826256.0,
      "text": "which will provide more finance for education."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 826280.0,
      "end_time": 829536.0,
      "text": "We will subsidize, or even eliminate completely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 829560.0,
      "end_time": 831496.0,
      "text": "interest payments on the loans"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 831520.0,
      "end_time": 833816.0,
      "text": "so that countries that commit to reforms"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 833840.0,
      "end_time": 835496.0,
      "text": "can borrow money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 835520.0,
      "end_time": 838976.0,
      "text": "reform their education system, and pay this money over time"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 839000.0,
      "end_time": 841560.0,
      "text": "while benefiting from a better-educated population."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 843000.0,
      "end_time": 847576.0,
      "text": "This solution has been recognized in the last G20 meeting in Germany,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 847600.0,
      "end_time": 851600.0,
      "text": "and so finally today education is on the international agenda."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 854160.0,
      "end_time": 856480.0,
      "text": "But let me bring this back to the personal level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 857520.0,
      "end_time": 859520.0,
      "text": "because this is where the impact lands."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 861120.0,
      "end_time": 865296.0,
      "text": "Without that decision to invest a young country&#39;s budget,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 865320.0,
      "end_time": 868936.0,
      "text": "20 percent of a young country&#39;s budget in education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 868960.0,
      "end_time": 872960.0,
      "text": "I would have never been able to go to school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 872120.0,
      "end_time": 874136.0,
      "text": "let alone in 2014"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 874160.0,
      "end_time": 876550.0,
      "text": "becoming a minister in the government"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 876800.0,
      "end_time": 878240.0,
      "text": "that successfully ended the transition phase."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 879480.0,
      "end_time": 882176.0,
      "text": "Tunisia&#39;s Nobel Peace Prize in 2015"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 882200.0,
      "end_time": 885576.0,
      "text": "as the only democracy that emerged from the Arab Spring"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 885600.0,
      "end_time": 888160.0,
      "text": "is a legacy to that bold leadership decision."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 890440.0,
      "end_time": 893216.0,
      "text": "Education is the civil rights struggle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 893240.0,
      "end_time": 895800.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s the human rights struggle of our generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 896640.0,
      "end_time": 898656.0,
      "text": "Quality education for all:"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 898680.0,
      "end_time": 901400.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s the freedom fight that we&#39;ve got to win."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 903160.0,
      "end_time": 904376.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 904400.0,
      "end_time": 908400.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
